{"id": "ChIJ82HOyF3HwoARR3EYGLH2jZ4", "rating": 4.7, "userRatingCount": 101, "displayName": {"text": "Temaki society", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ82HOyF3HwoARR3EYGLH2jZ4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aa1NVaG9jekYyZERSRmMwWllORGd3UjNsbk1tYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Finally tried this hand roll spot and it did not disappoint. Came during peak hours and waited a bit, but totally worth it. We ordered the 2person combo and everything was super fresh. The rice was perfectly seasoned and slightly warm, the nori was crisp, and the uni hand roll was outstanding — easily one of the best I’ve had. The soy marinated shrimp was also a standout. Small but stylish space, great quality overall. Would definitely come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Finally tried this hand roll spot and it did not disappoint. Came during peak hours and waited a bit, but totally worth it. We ordered the 2person combo and everything was super fresh. The rice was perfectly seasoned and slightly warm, the nori was crisp, and the uni hand roll was outstanding — easily one of the best I’ve had. The soy marinated shrimp was also a standout. Small but stylish space, great quality overall. Would definitely come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Cathy li", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112036890038445902114/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJ8aU7TQr8qNH3E8lFBw_Ic_B3xhCFqcAWvKjMK8uAAXwQaFI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-18T08:55:35.187501901Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aa1NVaG9jekYyZERSRmMwWllORGd3UjNsbk1tYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aa1NVaG9jekYyZERSRmMwWllORGd3UjNsbk1tYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c75dc8ce61f3:0x9e8df6b118187147"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ82HOyF3HwoARR3EYGLH2jZ4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ObWFVdHVTbkZPUWxSM1NtOXJSak5qU0RCdWJYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Amazing hand roll restaurants in DTLA with a speakeasy bar. They have a $88 couple combo which is great for dating and couple. The fish were so fresh and premium quality. The staffs are really friendly and loved the environment. The cocktails are straight from the bar and wasted great. We would definitely come back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Amazing hand roll restaurants in DTLA with a speakeasy bar. They have a $88 couple combo which is great for dating and couple. The fish were so fresh and premium quality. The staffs are really friendly and loved the environment. The cocktails are straight from the bar and wasted great. We would definitely come back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "bros gear", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106491851330957575451/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXpT0MZWvGa1tUQN8KghwEy-9FI2Q8gEG3UwC1DffRLezkPA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-02T18:42:13.557588273Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ObWFVdHVTbkZPUWxSM1NtOXJSak5qU0RCdWJYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ObWFVdHVTbkZPUWxSM1NtOXJSak5qU0RCdWJYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c75dc8ce61f3:0x9e8df6b118187147"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ82HOyF3HwoARR3EYGLH2jZ4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KZmMwdFhkVlZXUkZSME9EaGxURWgwTFY5bWRWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "10 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I’d seen this place pop up so many times and finally had to try it. They’re known for flying in fresh uni straight from Japan and using premium Japanese rice. Since uni quantities are limited, a lot of people said if you come late you’ll miss out, so I went right when they opened on a weekday lunch.\n\n5 Handroll Combo\n\nSpicy Tuna Roll: tuna with crispy onion\n\nSalmon Roll: fresh minced salmon\n\nScallop Roll: bay scallops with tobiko, juicy and crunchy\n\nYellowtail Roll: chopped yellowtail, tender and smooth\n\nBlue Crab Roll: blue crab with avocado\n\nThis set is such a deal at $29, considering each handroll is $7–8 if ordered separately. Freshness is guaranteed, nothing goes wrong here.\n\nOther handrolls I tried\n\nSpicy Yellowtail Roll: with jalapeño, cilantro, burdock, yuzu soy, and lemon zest—refreshing with a spicy kick\n\nBanh Mi Roll: Vietnamese banh mi spirit turned into sushi! Albacore tuna with pickled radish, chili, garlic chili oil, lime zest, and cilantro\n\nGolden Uni Roll: uni topped with 24K gold leaf, pickled wasabi, and shiso—sweet, creamy, totally worth it, and I got uni from a freshly opened box\n\nCUT Roll: tuna, uni, and caviar layered beautifully\n\nLobster Roll (seasonal): with peanut sauce, hoisin, sriracha, green onion, and crispy onion—rich and Southeast Asian-inspired\n\nUni Toast\nJapanese shokupan toasted crisp, topped with herb mayo, ikura, nori, and uni. One luxurious bite!\n\nMarinated Shrimp\nPacked with flavor. I’m always a sucker for marinated shrimp, and seeing it here was a happy surprise.\n\nOverall, the ingredients are super fresh and the prices fair for what they offer. It’s not fine dining but easily one of the best in this style. I’ll definitely be back to try their sashimi bowls for a quick lunch.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I’d seen this place pop up so many times and finally had to try it. They’re known for flying in fresh uni straight from Japan and using premium Japanese rice. Since uni quantities are limited, a lot of people said if you come late you’ll miss out, so I went right when they opened on a weekday lunch.\n\n5 Handroll Combo\n\nSpicy Tuna Roll: tuna with crispy onion\n\nSalmon Roll: fresh minced salmon\n\nScallop Roll: bay scallops with tobiko, juicy and crunchy\n\nYellowtail Roll: chopped yellowtail, tender and smooth\n\nBlue Crab Roll: blue crab with avocado\n\nThis set is such a deal at $29, considering each handroll is $7–8 if ordered separately. Freshness is guaranteed, nothing goes wrong here.\n\nOther handrolls I tried\n\nSpicy Yellowtail Roll: with jalapeño, cilantro, burdock, yuzu soy, and lemon zest—refreshing with a spicy kick\n\nBanh Mi Roll: Vietnamese banh mi spirit turned into sushi! Albacore tuna with pickled radish, chili, garlic chili oil, lime zest, and cilantro\n\nGolden Uni Roll: uni topped with 24K gold leaf, pickled wasabi, and shiso—sweet, creamy, totally worth it, and I got uni from a freshly opened box\n\nCUT Roll: tuna, uni, and caviar layered beautifully\n\nLobster Roll (seasonal): with peanut sauce, hoisin, sriracha, green onion, and crispy onion—rich and Southeast Asian-inspired\n\nUni Toast\nJapanese shokupan toasted crisp, topped with herb mayo, ikura, nori, and uni. One luxurious bite!\n\nMarinated Shrimp\nPacked with flavor. I’m always a sucker for marinated shrimp, and seeing it here was a happy surprise.\n\nOverall, the ingredients are super fresh and the prices fair for what they offer. It’s not fine dining but easily one of the best in this style. I’ll definitely be back to try their sashimi bowls for a quick lunch.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rey Chou", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108269752771139309175/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTm62S5RE4wSu68m2b70FX6TX5x1f_v0wf9nlxZ5rfA3wh6w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-08-25T23:49:11.552486698Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KZmMwdFhkVlZXUkZSME9EaGxURWgwTFY5bWRWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21KZmMwdFhkVlZXUkZSME9EaGxURWgwTFY5bWRWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c75dc8ce61f3:0x9e8df6b118187147"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ82HOyF3HwoARR3EYGLH2jZ4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21scmRXZFVMVmxMVFhwQ2NURlhiMUJzTUhsNlYyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Perfect hand rolls awesome pictoral menu so you can see exactly what you're gonna get. The fish is next level fresh and all the little details are done right. The tostada I got had so much fish and was delicious. Highly recommend", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Perfect hand rolls awesome pictoral menu so you can see exactly what you're gonna get. The fish is next level fresh and all the little details are done right. The tostada I got had so much fish and was delicious. Highly recommend", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Risknc (risknc)", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105103422155337426522/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOZY_7dvkSTqoMSZyrThNLSY0n8WX4ahB472a0aRlKosRl0D8xLQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-06T04:56:10.798892556Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21scmRXZFVMVmxMVFhwQ2NURlhiMUJzTUhsNlYyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21scmRXZFVMVmxMVFhwQ2NURlhiMUJzTUhsNlYyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c75dc8ce61f3:0x9e8df6b118187147"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ82HOyF3HwoARR3EYGLH2jZ4/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUN3MDU2alBREAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "If you're a fan of fresh, high-quality hand rolls, Temaki Society is an absolute must-try! From the moment you walk in, you can tell this place takes their craft seriously--clean, modern decor, friendly staff, and an open bar-style seating where you can watch the chefs prepare each roll to perfection. If you love hand rolls and appreciate top-notch ingredients, Temaki Society delivers an exceptional experience. Prices are reasonable for the quality, and the attention to detail is impeccable. Definitely adding this to my regular rotation!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "If you're a fan of fresh, high-quality hand rolls, Temaki Society is an absolute must-try! From the moment you walk in, you can tell this place takes their craft seriously--clean, modern decor, friendly staff, and an open bar-style seating where you can watch the chefs prepare each roll to perfection. If you love hand rolls and appreciate top-notch ingredients, Temaki Society delivers an exceptional experience. Prices are reasonable for the quality, and the attention to detail is impeccable. Definitely adding this to my regular rotation!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ruby Han", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106192687901086909912/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZFB8rhf43nMZ9Na13WC-RC-MzthgzzknQVqY8YW66y36Lmg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-03-21T01:28:56.758017Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUN3MDU2alBREAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUN3MDU2alBREAE!2m1!1s0x80c2c75dc8ce61f3:0x9e8df6b118187147"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ82HOyF3HwoARR3EYGLH2jZ4/photos/AWCwydifRG6RVb-lvTWBZ27GJf6MrJ7W-ZcsLVAmD3lcoPifMkuvljjFFvobluGQ6BM5OZGge1uMgETZcZd7gi3z5QjvHEeMVo7_e7xS3Y0S5kZhsTJdGjRKNiXu1Sq6y8H8j9L8ZHaEvCyn88T8-XNNfU9cutnQPf85bzONzJ0yrIFOh0km92PEzHK3TjfKENLv7lBcqjB4ecPhmdQTpqlgKZMDEvc3CEdc9-49zLEStnh15NS1sL8ORxxFfVzlqaRep_dvV_yg3Mt80K1iigK0BXS85e2JwFxPNBXhzt3AOYdVgvHNTnSUUwlFii0eCiL6tbA3jmBmpWf0IBFMp66rOfSPGxFir9gLbVs3kReTdacajf2GyLjhDqGL5TAPcl2y4-WWcDRJdT41tg63bqMY5VA-kNjsnNFPCMkfi7K4tADJxPPYTds3Dnyd9jhW32R1", "widthPx": 3600, "heightPx": 4800, "aut